@Everybody complaining about how boring it is:

Who gives a shit about your opinion? None of these people do. You're trying to act cool. Save the time it takes to type those comments up and spend them on something more useful like learning to not complain about shit that is FREE. Nobody asks for your opinion. I know extremezone doesn't wanna see these comments on his/her torrent uploads. If you don't like it, don't comment. Simple as that.

I do, however, want to thank extremezone for amazing uploads all across TPB. Thanks for the 10/10 uploads!
